==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fluidal
<hw>Flu"id*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Pertaining to a
fluid, or to its flowing motion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Fluidal structure</b></col> <fld>(Geol.)</fld>, <cd>the
structure characteristic of certain volcanic rocks in which the
arrangement of the minute crystals shows the lines of flow of thew
molten material before solidification; -- also called <altname>fluxion
structure</altname>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fluidity</ent>⟦br⟧
